## Offline Training Pipeline (train.py)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["📂 data/job_descriptions.csv\n(up to 1.7GB raw CSV)"]
    B["Sample 50K jobs\nrandom_state=42"]
    C["get_combined_text()\nTitle + Skills + Desc[:500]\npreprocess_text applied"]

    D["TfidfVectorizer.fit()\non first 2000 rows\nmax_features=1000\nngrams 1-2\nstop_words=english"]
    E["TfidfVectorizer.transform()\non all 50K in 256-row chunks"]
    F["scipy.sparse.vstack()\nFinal: 50K × 1000 sparse"]

    G["SentenceTransformer\nall-MiniLM-L6-v2\ndevice = CUDA or CPU"]
    H["Encode 256 rows\nat a time"]
    I["Save bert_chunk_XXXX.npy\nto disk instantly\nfrees RAM per batch"]
    J["np.vstack all chunks\nFinal: 50K × 384 dense"]

    K["💾 Save Artifacts"]
    L["tfidf.pkl"]
    M["job_vectors.pkl"]
    N["bert_job_vectors.pkl"]
    O["jobs.pkl\n(metadata only)"]

    A --> B --> C
    C --> D --> E --> F
    C --> G --> H --> I --> J
    F --> K
    J --> K
    K --> L & M & N & O
```

