## Hybrid Recommendation Engine — 3-Stage Pipeline (recommend.py)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    INPUT["📄 Resume Text\n+ Skills + Experience"]

    subgraph STAGE1["Stage 1 — Fast Candidate Filtering (All 50K jobs)"]
        S1A["TF-IDF transform(resume)\n→ sparse 1×1000 vector"]
        S1B["cosine_similarity(resume_tfidf, job_vectors)\n→ 50K scores  raw [0,1]"]
        S1C["BERT encode(resume)\n→ dense 384-dim vector"]
        S1D["cosine_similarity(resume_bert, bert_job_vectors)\n→ 50K scores  raw [0,1]"]
        S1E["draft_score = 0.7×semantic + 0.3×tfidf\n+ uniform jitter(0, 0.01) for tie-breaking"]
        S1F["nlargest(1000, draft_score)\n→ Deduplicate by title+company"]
    end

    subgraph STAGE2["Stage 2 — Detailed Re-ranking (Top 1000 only)"]
        S2A["Extract job skill lists\nfrom top-1000 rows"]
        S2B["BERT encode all unique\njob skills (batched)"]
        S2C["BERT encode\nresume skills"]
        S2D["sim_matrix = dot(resume_skill_embs, job_skill_embs.T)\ncount(sim >= 0.75) / len(job_skills)\n→ skill_score per job"]
        S2E["experience_score\n= clip(resume_exp / job_exp, 0, 1)"]
    end

    subgraph STAGE3["Stage 3 — Final Hybrid Score"]
        S3["final_score =\n0.60 × semantic_score\n+ 0.15 × tfidf_score\n+ 0.20 × skill_score\n+ 0.05 × exp_score\n+ 0.001 × draft_score (tiebreak)"]
    end

    subgraph DEDUP["Diversity-Aware Deduplication"]
        D1["Sort by final_score DESC"]
        D2["seen_listings set\n(title + company + location)"]
        D3["title_counts dict\nMAX_PER_TITLE = 5"]
        D4["Yield until top_n collected"]
    end

    INPUT --> STAGE1
    S1A --> S1B
    S1C --> S1D
    S1B & S1D --> S1E --> S1F
    S1F --> STAGE2
    S2A --> S2B
    S2C --> S2D
    S2B --> S2D
    S2D & S2E --> STAGE3
    S3 --> DEDUP
    D1 --> D2 --> D3 --> D4
    D4 --> RESULTS["✅ Top-N Unique Jobs"]
```

