## Collaborative Filtering Flow (collaborative.py)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["User interacts with a job\nclickweight=1  saveweight=2  applyweight=3"]
    B["POST /interaction\n→ save_interaction()"]
    C["Append row to\ndata/interactions.csv"]

    D["get_cf_recommendations(user_id)"]
    E["load_interactions()\nfrom CSV"]
    F["build_user_item_matrix()\ngroupby user+job → pivot\nrows=users  cols=jobs\nvalues=max weight  fillna=0"]

    G["cosine_similarity(matrix.T)\nCompare job columns\n→ Item-Item similarity matrix\nshape: n_jobs × n_jobs"]

    H["user_ratings = matrix.loc[user_id]\nget all jobs user interacted with"]
    I["For each unseen job:\npred_score = Σ sim×rating / Σ sim\nweighted sum of similarities"]
    J["Sort by pred_score DESC\n→ Top-N CF recommendations"]

    K["get_hybrid_recommendations()\nnorm_content = final_score / max\nnorm_cf = cf_score / max\nhybrid = 0.6×content + 0.4×CF"]

    COLD["⚠️ Cold Start:\nUser has NO interactions\n→ CF returns empty\n→ 100% content-based scoring"]

    A --> B --> C
    D --> E --> F --> G --> H --> I --> J --> K
    C -.->|next request| E
    D -.->|new user| COLD
```

