## Real-Time Job Search Flow (JSearch API)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant JS as JSearch API (RapidAPI)
    participant ML as recommend_jobs()

    U->>FE: Enter query + location + paste resume
    FE->>API: POST /recommend/realtime/{user_id}\n(query, location, resume_text, page)

    API->>JS: GET jsearch.p.rapidapi.com/search\n?query="python developer jobs in NYC"
    JS-->>API: JSON list of live job postings

    API->>API: Convert to DataFrame\nid, Job Title, Company, Location,\nJob Description, apply_url

    API->>API: tfidf.transform(job_descriptions)\n→ realtime TF-IDF vectors

    API->>ML: recommend_jobs(resume, realtime_df,\ntfidf, realtime_vectors,\nbert=None  skipped for speed)

    ML-->>API: Ranked DataFrame with final_score

    API->>API: Paginate results\npage × page_size

    API-->>FE: {recommendations, total, page}
    FE-->>U: Live job cards with apply_url links
```

