## Component Responsibility Summary

| File | Layer | Responsibility |
|------|-------|---------------|
| `train.py` | Offline | Fit TF-IDF, encode BERT, save artifacts |
| `api.py` | API | Route requests, load artifacts, auth middleware |
| `src/recommend.py` | ML Core | 3-stage hybrid ranking pipeline |
| `src/vectorize.py` | Embedding | TF-IDF + Sentence-BERT wrappers, cosine sim |
| `src/preprocess.py` | NLP | Text cleaning, entity extraction, semantic skill overlap |
| `src/collaborative.py` | CF | Interaction logging, user-item matrix, item-item CF, hybrid blend |
| `src/auth.py` | Security | Password hashing, JWT create/verify, OAuth2 flow |
| `src/llm_parser.py` | NLP | Parse resume → structured JSON via LLM |
| `src/llm_explainer.py` | NLP | Generate human-readable job match explanations |
| `src/real_jobs.py` | External | JSearch API client utilities |
| `frontend/` | UI | React dashboard, auth modal, job cards, search |

